    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Pseudosesarma glabrum n. sp., holotype: male (13.8 × 12.0 mm) (CUSAT 2016 - 1), India. A, overall dorsal view; B, dorsal view of carapace; C, left third maxilliped." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/847558/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.847560>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Pseudosesarma glabrum n. sp., holotype male (13.8 × 12.0 mm) (CUSAT 2016 - 1), India. A, frontal view of cephalothorax; B, outer view of left chela; C, anterior thoracic sternum and pleon." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/847560/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.847562>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Pseudosesarma glabrum n. sp., holotype male (13.8 × 12.0 mm) (CUSAT 2016 - 1), India. A, pleon; B, dorsal view of left G 1; C, ventro-mesial view of left G 1; D, ventral view of left G 1; E, left G 2. Scales: A = 2.0 mm; B – E = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/847562/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.847564>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Colour in life. Pseudosesarma glabrum n. sp., paratype male (16.5 × 14.5 mm) (CUSAT 2016 - 3), India. A, dorsal overall view; B, frontal view showing cephalothorax and chelae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/847564/files/figure.png" ;
